  "body": "Hi,\r\n\r\nI'm trying to port [tornado_cash](https://github.com/tornadocash/tornado-core) to hardhat but I had the following issue.\r\n\r\nLibrary called `Hasher` that is located under `contracts/MerkleTreeWithHistory.sol` when compiled using hardhat doesn't output bytecode in [artifacts file](https://gist.github.com/filippetroviccc/5e3592168fa8945e20beef0fae09e6e5).\r\n\r\nThe same project, compiled with `truffle compile` has bytecode inside [build file](https://gist.github.com/filippetroviccc/27375660693962e995861136f72fe9b4).\r\n\r\n### Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\n1. Clone [tornado_cash](https://github.com/tornadocash/tornado-core)\r\n2. Run `npx hardhat` -> create empty project.\r\n3. Change compiler version to `0.5.17`\r\n4. Run `npm install --save hardhat`\r\n5. Run `npm install`\r\n6. Run `npm run build:circuit`\r\n7. Run `npx hardhat compile`\r\n\r\nCheck file located under `./artifacts/contracts/MerkleTreeWithHistory.sol/Hasher.json`",
